Enhance your Smart Home experience with OSAIO's products.

If you own an Alexa Echo Show, you can ask Alexa Echo Show to display the live view from your OSAIO.

Follow the steps here to connect your OSAIO account to Alexa:
1. Download the "OSAIO" app from the app store;
2. Register a OSAIO account to add your devices;
3. Configure your devices and name the devices;
4. Download the "Alexa" app from the app store;
5. Configure Alexa Echo Show in the "Alexa" app;
6. Search for "OSAIO" from the skills category in the "Alexa" app;
7. Enable "OSAIO" skill, and you'll be navigated to OSAIO's login page;
8. Log into your OSAIO account to finish.


Once the "OSAIO" Skill is enabled, simply ask Alexa to control your OSAIO devices by their names. For example:
“Alexa, show (name of device)"
“Alexa, stop"

If you experience any problems while using this skill, please contact us at app-support@osaio.net
